text: La Chapelle-Bouëxic () is a commune in the Ille-et-Vilaine department in Brittany in northwestern France. It is located southwest of Rennes between Pont-Péan and Guer. ==Population== Inhabitants of La Chapelle-Bouëxic are called Chapellois in French. ==See also== *Communes of the Ille-et-Vilaine department ==References== *INSEE ==External links== * Cultural Heritage Category:Communes of Ille-et-Vilaine
title: La Chapelle-Bouëxic
